  "text": "Approaches such as iterative trace ratio (ITR) maximization or decomposed Newton's method (DNM) can be used for this purpose and it has been shown that trace ratio maximization performs better than generalized eigen decomposition in supervised dimensionality reduction [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
